set tabstop=4 "width of <TAB> displays as
set softtabstop=4 "backspace after pressing <TAB> will remove up to this many space
set shiftwidth=4 "number of spaces to use for each step of (auto)indent
set expandtab "convert <TAB> key-presses to spaces
set scrolloff=8 "starts scrolling 8 from top or bottom mouse wheel
set signcolumn=yes "makes column that shows E for error
set colorcolumn=80 "highlight column to show when you're maybe indenting a bit too far
set nowrap "stops lines wrapping
